item.title: Paddock Stand
item.description: If you’re a motorcycle enthusiast, you know how important it is to have a good paddock stand.

item.title: The Arrival
item.description: Today I received my Yamaha MT-25 from Puncak Alam Motoworld Sdn Bhd. I decided a few months ago to ride to work hence I am on the quest to find a suitable motorcycle that can fulfill my needs.
